  <brief_title>Anti-diabetic Effects of Persimmon Leaf Extract</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Eight-week, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Crossover Clinical Trial of Persimmon Leaf Extract on Anti-diabetes</official_title>
  <sponsors>
