  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators performed a 8-week, randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled crossover
      human trial to evaluate the efficacy and safety of persimmon leaf extract on blood glucose.
      The investigators measures changes in diabetes associated parameters, including fasting blood
      glucose, postprandial blood glucose, insulin, C-peptide and HbA1c.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
